summary: This is an FBI electronic communication document dated June 27, 2025, which serves to open a subfile under the case ID 72-MM-113327-VICTIM, related to a transparency project concerning victims. The document is administrative in nature, initiating a subfile for record-keeping or investigative purposes.

events.title: Subfile Opening for Victim Transparency Project
events.description: An FBI electronic communication was drafted to open a subfile under case ID 72-MM-113327-VICTIM, related to a transparency project concerning victims.

keyFacts: The document is an FBI electronic communication dated June 27, 2025.
Its purpose is to open a subfile under the case ID 72-MM-113327-VICTIM.
The subfile is related to a 'Transparency Project - Victims'.
The document is marked as UNCLASSIFIED.
It is an administrative action to initiate a subfile for record-keeping or investigative purposes related to victims.
